sentences: Hiromi Haneda (羽田裕美, Haneda Hiromi, born October 11, 1981) is a Japanese former pianist under Giza Studio label.
In 2007 she appeared as a pianist in Memorial Concerts of Zard.
In 2008 she released her first album Kokoro wo Hiraite: Zard Piano Classics  Her last update on her personal blog was in December 2012.
